{"tid":1564805,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你地班友唔好因為一個共和黨議員說話打曬飛機啦。","createTime":"2019-09-13T02:05:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T03:07:35.000Z","uid":62011,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"22f917c3499138612c2b970f5c44622848f4faba","tid":1564805,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T02:05:41.000Z","msg":"共和黨大佬: 連登仔唔駛太擔心senate hold阻止香港人權法通過<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1564657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1564657</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一日未過人權法，都要抱住一個悲觀既心態，不斷向美國表達民意/或者調翻轉諗，既然共和當唔阻止，係咪更加乘勝追擊??? 令件事更家穩陣。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一、大家要繼續係唔同國會議員留言：</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n呢到集合曬所有議員TWITTER：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/cspan/lists/members-of-congress?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcspan%2Flists%2Fmembers-of-congress%3Fs%3D09&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmL6sSahl6lMEnfwETMIwf14%3D&h=51b9b170\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/cspan/lists/members-of-congress?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n行動指引：<br />\n<br />\n=====【目標】=====<br />\n－向美國參眾兩院請願，加速通過《香港人權及民主法案》2019，令美國可向中共及香港施壓，監督香港確立雙普選，達到自治。<br />\n－對象：參眾兩院議員<br />\n<br />\n=====【主要訊息】=====<br />\n1.) 香港人支持法案通過。(PLEASE PASS Hong Kong Human Right and Democracy Act)<br />\n2.) 香港人要求雙普選。(We want dual sufferage to select our legislators(senator) and Chief Executive of HK)<br />\n3.) 如無法達至民主化，港人明白和已準備接受全面制裁。<br />\n(Please impose sanction on HK if necessary for Democracy)<br />\n3.) 中共港共破壞香港自治，而且向市民施暴，情況危急。<br />\n(The CCP is destroying HK autonomy and violating HK people with violence.<br />\n4.) 香港人乃反共先鋒，值得世界支持。<br />\n(HK is willing to be a bridgehead, as to counter against the CCP.<br />\n<br />\n=====【注意事項】=====<br />\n1.) 此法案乃兩黨合作(bipartisan)進行，切切避免將兩黨之爭拉入香港議題，不要和特朗普總統，共和黨或民主黨割席。<br />\n2.) 如見到有人罵Trump或有人罵民主黨，不要捲入罵戰，繼續跟他們說【主要訊息】就行。<br />\n3.) 記住你的目標是參眾兩院，這次是兩黨都想搶功勞。群眾罵Trump，會令民主黨更高興地推法案，反之亦然，毋須介懷。<br />\n4.) 落HASHTAG。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">二、所有遊行集會，都要唱埋美國國歌，舉美國旗。</span></strong>係街唱，哩入商場鬼睇到阿???<br />\n<br />\n三、真美國人(綠卡、入籍、美國人)戰線<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wJj6Bh9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwJj6Bh9.jpg&h=b802e391&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd3457b212506b0c46ca6ff220c5d415f1bd8145","tid":1564805,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T02:06:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f0a38b68beed82f7094a98adf5e1fe9629c37d9e","tid":1564805,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T02:06:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"b78f38da582d4239c203791b146832f11f640410","tid":1564805,"uid":275588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T02:06:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74063416d13c715647ecd85171588f260eaafd35","tid":1564805,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T02:06:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">913中秋要人!!</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6Tnu54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%